DOC.brief_summary: The primary objective of this study is assess the Tear Film break-up time (TBUT) in mild to moderate dry eye subjects.
DOC.brief_title: Comparative Efficacy of SYSTANE® ULTRA vs Optive™ in Improving Tear Film Break-up Time
DOC.detailed_description: The primary objective of this study is assess the tear film break-up time in mild to moderate dry eye subjects.
DOC.criteria: Corrected VA of 0.6 LogMar or better OU Exclusion: Topical ocular medication use Presence of Ocular conditions (blepharitis, conjunctival infections, etc)
DOC.keyword: Dry eye or lubricant eye drops
